 Reproduction in Plants
 
  Methods of reproduction
    Fission - Protozoan Bacteria
    Budding - Coelentrates Yeast
    Fragmentation - Flatworms Algae
    Spores - Fungi
    Sexual reproduction - Mammals
    Pollination and fertilization - Flowering plants
    
